These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, november, july, may, march
5 different games are played: go, backgammon, snooker, domino, whist
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, iris, tulip, azalea, lily
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, electronic, dubstep, ambient, reggae
 1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 2. the fan of reggae is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person playing go##1
 4. the fan of pop is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person who growsiris is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fan of pop##1
11. the person who growsiris is the fan of pop##1
12. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Birthday         | november  | february    | may | july    | march  |
| Game   | backgammon  | go | snooker | domino | whist  |
| Flower           | daffodil     | lily     | azalea  | iris   | tulip    |
| Music-Genre         | dubstep | ambient    | electronic | pop  | reggae |

