.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, milk, sprite, juice
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, baking, board-games, collecting, dancing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo, dannemann, ritmeester, blend
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, soccer, rugby, cricket, sailing
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the dannemann-smoker##1
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking milk##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
12. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Beverage          | milk        | juice | lemonade     | sprite      | soy-milk  |
| Hobby           | baking   | board-games | dancing    | collecting | gardening |
| Cigar   | dannemann | ritmeester     | blend | bongani    | tiparillo  |
| Sport   | cricket     | soccer | tennis    | sailing      | rugby    |

