.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, scrabble, poker, chess
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, epic, thriller, zombie, superhero
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, soccer, chess-polo, baseball
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, cat, hedgehog, goat, snake
 1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is chess-polo##1
 9. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching family movies##1
12. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
13. the person playing poker is the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Game      | poker          | scrabble  | mah-jongg       | bridge     | chess      |
| Movie-Genre         | epic | superhero | zombie  | thriller   | family    |
| Sport   | basketball        | baseball | swimming | chess-polo    | soccer   |
| Pet     | rabbit   | hedgehog | snake      | cat | goat |

