.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, december, november, april, july
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, weightlifting, basketball, parkour, rugby
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, prince, cain, dunhill, bluemaster
The people have 5 different hobbies: woodworking, baking, video-games, singing, reading
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the prince-smoker is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the game-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
 9. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is the cain-smoker##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Birthday          | april        | march       | november | december   | july  |
| Sport   | rugby | basketball | weightlifting | baseball   | parkour |
