.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-5::.
City: hamburg, edinburgh, rome, san-francisco, colone
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, january, february, april, march
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: musical, epic, mystery, crime, action
There are 5 different nationalities: french, spanish, turkish, indian, dutch
 1. the person watching epic movies is the turkish##1
 2. the turkish is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the dutch is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is the french##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
12. the indian is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| City          | edinburgh    | colone  | rome | hamburg    | san-francisco      |
| Birthday           | march | february | may  | april | january |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery           | epic      | action      | crime        | musical     |
| Nationality         | spanish         | turkish  | french   | indian       | dutch  |

