.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-6::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, motorbike, train, car
5 different pets are kept: hamster, frog, mouse, goldfish, horse
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dunhill, prince, fonseca, davidoff
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, pop, jazz, house, classical
 1. the owner of the hamster is the fan of classical##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 3. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
 6. the owner of the frog is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of jazz##1
 8. the fan of house is the fonseca-smoker##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
12. the fan of house is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Transport         | motorbike  | car  | ship    | jet-ski | train |
| Pet   | hamster        | mouse  | goldfish | frog      | horse        |
| Cigar   | dunhill       | fonseca  | prince   | davidoff | cain     |
| Music-Genre         | classical | house | jazz | pop  | gospel      |

