 4. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 5. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
