 9. the person eating avocado is the person traveling to london##1
10. the person eating lime is in the middle##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person eating lime##1
12. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
14. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
