.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-9::.
5 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, hamster, chinchilla, mouse
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, snooker, monopoly, chess
The people have 5 different jobs:  police-officer, accountant, pilot, designer, teacher
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, strawberry, orange, tomato, lettuce
 1. the teacher is the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person playing canasta is the owner of the bird##1
 3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the police-officer##1
 4. the person playing chess is the person eating cauliflower##1
 5. the designer is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person eating cauliflower is the accountant##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is the accountant##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
10. the person eating orange is the owner of the hamster##1
11. the person playing monopoly is the pilot##1
12. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person playing chess##1
13. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating orange##1
14. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |      4       |     5      |
| Pet      | mouse       | bird   | chinchilla        | ferret          | hamster      |
| Game         | chess | canasta | snooker  | monopoly | mah-jongg |
| Job   | accountant  | police-officer    | teacher       | pilot         | designer        |
| Food     | cauliflower    | tomato    | lettuce | strawberry         | orange  |

