.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, december, may, january, february
The people have 5 different jobs:  writer, journalist, accountant, social-worker, lawyer
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, alhambra, havana, baccarat, swisher
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, skiing, weightlifting, badminton, tennis
 1. the journalist is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 3. the social-worker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 5. the writer is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 7. the journalist is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the writer##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the lawyer##1
12. the accountant is the baccarat-smoker##1
13. the lawyer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Birthday      | june      | december       | february         | january  | may |
| Job   | accountant  | social-worker | journalist | writer  | lawyer  |
| Cigar   | baccarat    | alhambra    | pall-mall        | swisher | havana     |
| Sport           | skiing | weightlifting      | water-polo       | badminton   | tennis   |

