.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, september, december, march, july
There 5 different types of food: cherry, lemon, zucchini, radish, papaya
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, hiking, card-games, fishing, dancing
5 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, go, billiard, mah-jongg
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating lemon##1
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is the person eating papaya##1
11. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating radish##1
12. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
13. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
