City: san-francisco, nizza, paris, prague, boston
House: modern, gothic-revival, futuristic, wooden, colonial
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 2. the colonial house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is the modern house##1
 4. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 6. the colonial house is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the colonial house is on the left of the modern house##1
 9. the modern house is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the colonial house##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is rowing##1
13. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
