.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, biathlon, snowboarding, lacrosse, weightlifting
The people have 5 different jobs:  paramedic, writer, nurse, dancer, project-manager
City: boston, liverpool, miami, venice, berlin
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, sunflower, marigold, dahlia, rose
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
 2. the dancer is the person who growsiris##1
 3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the dancer##1
 4. the paramedic is the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the nurse is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 9. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
11. the paramedic is on the far right##1
12. the project-manager is in the middle##1
13. the person traveling to boston is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
14. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Sport      | biathlon | lacrosse   | snowboarding    | handball       | weightlifting |
| Job   | nurse           | writer   | project-manager   | dancer       | paramedic  |
| City   | liverpool       | boston | miami | venice     | berlin   |
| Flower     | marigold    | sunflower   | dahlia   | iris | rose   |

 